<br>
The gypsie camp in NK, the bazaar, and the arena do NOT have soulbinders.<br>
<br>
Highpass keep does not appear to have a soulbinder. I do not think highpass hold has one either.<br>
<br>
Shadowhaven does have a soulbinder (near the water).<br>
<br>
The soulbinder in Painwheel is not accessable to anyone with bad painwheel faction . So if you're headed the the warrens or stonebrunt get bound in Erudin or get someone to bind you near the warrens.<br>
