Inert Potion Quest<br>
This quest takes place in Erudin Palace, on Odus. This quest is for those that are un-KoS to erudins.<br>
<br>
+ Coalition of Trade Folk Ill<br>
+ Coalition of Tradefolk <br>
+ The Freeport Militia<br>
+ Corrupt Qeynos Guards<br>
+ Carson McCabe<br>
